Name: Fish. Love. Danger.
About the game: A cute HARDCORE arcade game about a fish in love. There are a lot of interesting things in this little game: - a kind story about love and courage - hand-drawn graphics - nice animation - hard puzzles - simple mouse control, but hardcore levels. Good luck!
